definitions.definition: Of or pertaining to a vestige or remnant ; like a trace from the past.
Not fully developed in mature animals.
Of a vestigial structure ; that has lost all or most of its original function in the course of evolution.

main_definition: Of or pertaining to a vestige or remnant ; like a trace from the past.
secondary_definitions: Not fully developed in mature animals.
( evolutionary theory ) Of a vestigial structure ; that has lost all or most of its original function in the course of evolution.
